reviewText: DVD skipped. Had to print return label, ship back, to get refund. Not worth the trouble. Download in iTunes or just watch parts of it on YouTube.

It's a great little concert, 5 songs from " The Bird of Music,"and 2 songs from "Verses of Comfort,Asurance & Salvation. This trio of Erika, Heather and Annie are like watching and listening to angels. I could watch and listen to them all day. If I had only one group that I could listen to, it would definitely  be Au Revoir Simone.
  D.M.
